data.description: A beautiful 2br/2bath, ranch home sits on 2acres with 2/3rds being wooded. The home consists of a very charming 3 season sunroom, where you can watch the abundant wildlife while having your morning coffee.  Right outside the sunroom is a relaxing deck to enjoy your barbecues with friends and family.  The kitchen is adorable, it comes with all the appliances.!!  An oversized three stall garage with plenty work space for your hobbies.  The garage has a large concrete approach and horseshoe driveway.  The home has a whole house generator so you don't have to worry about loosing power.  The property is very close to the White Pine Trails for walking and biking.  Close to town and the 131 fwy.  You don't want to pass this one up.  It is immaculate with nothing you have to do but move in.
